A 29-year-old driver of a Vauxhall Vectra was arrested on suspicion of causing death by dangerous driving and failing to stop, while a 78-year-old driver of a Fiat Panda was arrested on suspicion of drinking and driving and failing to stop.
West Midlands Police appealed for witnesses to contact them.
